Ok, so yea it isn't the best textured map, and yea it isn't the most original map, and yea it isn't the best map, but I made it under an hour ( i'll probably release a better version).

Let's see, well you it's one of those downward surf maps, like you slide down.

That's pretty much it, I guess. There's a buyzone at spawn..... um, it's kinda short.

And yes I made it (it says dynamic on ct spawn).

Ya know to be honest, the map is crap, but I've gotten quite abit of praise from it, and I decided to put it on here.. atleast it's fun.

Make sure you have sv_airaccelerate to 100 atleast

            -Dynamic
